item.title: CVE-2022-22681|2024-09-16T16:18:01.296Z -- synology -- photo%20station
item.description: Session fixation vulnerability in access control management in Synology Photo Station before 6.8.16-3506 allows remote attackers to bypass security constraint via unspecified vectors.

item.title: CVE-2017-12080|2024-09-16T16:58:09.999Z -- synology -- photo%20station
item.description: An information exposure vulnerability in default HTTP configuration file in Synology Photo Station before 6.8.1-3458 and before 6.3-2970 allows remote attackers to obtain sensitive system information via .htaccess file.
